Qiew - Hex viewer/editor, disassembler, with capabilities to read PE file format and display useful information for malware analysis. 
available formats by now: PE, bootsector, binary (default)

Written in python+qt, should work on Windows, Linux, MAC OSX.
Terminus font is needed: http://sourceforge.net/projects/terminus-font/files/terminus-font-4.39/terminus-font-4.39.exe/download

read wiki page for more information: https://github.com/mtivadar/qiew/wiki

